Perfect for dinner or lunch, loaded fries are a hearty meal to enjoy with your loved ones. Loaded fries consisting of French fries covered in cheese, with the possible addition of various other toppings like vegetables, beef, and shrimp. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Bake or fry the French fries beforehand until golden brown and put in a baking pan. Step 2 Fry the bacon and sprinkle on the fries. Step 3 Cover them with grated cheese, then place them back in the oven to melt the cheese. Serve hot and enjoy with a cold beverage and guacamole.